<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021294-0051 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 012678 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 12, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 2; Metro Desk 
