 Huntington Beach 95, Marina 53 -- Tony Gonzalez scored 37 points and had 11 
rebounds for Huntington Beach (17-9, 11-3), which finished second in league. 
Andy Nieto scored 14 points for host Marina (10-16, 4-10). 
</P>
