<P>
AND WHILE WE'RE ON THE SUBJECT OF IRISH . . . 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Gene Wojciechowski just doesn't get it. Sure, Notre Dame was probably behind 
the Kerrigan hit. And if you study the photos long enough, you'll see six 
Catholic nuns, a leprechaun and Touchdown Jesus disassembling their AK-47s just 
