<HEADLINE>
<P>
SCHIZOPHRENIA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Ray Loynd's Jan. 15 review ("Diana Ross in 'Darkness' Spotlight") of the ABC 
television drama "Out of Darkness," which he described as ". . . Ross' 
shattering portrait of a woman's battle with paranoia/schizophrenia," contains 
one very disturbing sentence: 
</P>
