<P>
 Chad Bickley, a six-foot junior point guard for Santa Maria Valley Christian 
Academy, scored a Southern Section record 89 points -- including a record 20 
three-point shots -- to lead the Lions to a 130-48 Coast Valley League victory 
over host Cuyama Valley. 
</P>
